15 WHEREAS, many graduates of the Luella High School NJROTC Program go on to serve
16 in the military while others uphold the program's values in various leadership careers,
17 creating a lasting impact on their communities and beyond; and
18 WHEREAS, the Luella High School NJROTC Program remains a cornerstone of excellence,
19 shaping the future leaders of tomorrow through discipline, service, and leadership.
20 NOW, THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES that
21 the members of this body commend the Luella High School NJROTC Program for its
22 decades of service to the youth of Locust Grove, Georgia, and extend sincere best wishes for
23 continued success.
24 BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED that the Clerk of the House of Representatives is authorized
25 and directed to make an appropriate copy of this resolution available for distribution to the
26 Luella High School NJROTC Program.
